<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <title>Power of Attorney</title>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        color: #000;
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        -webkit-user-select: none;
        -moz-user-select: none;
        -ms-user-select: none;
        user-select: none;
      }

      .page {
        background: white;
        width: 21cm;
        min-height: 29.7cm;
        padding: 2cm;
        margin: 1cm auto;
        border: 1px solid #d3d3d3;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .section {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: justify;
      }

      .signature-section {
        margin-top: 40px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        body {
          background-color: white;
        }
        .page {
          width: 100%;
          min-height: auto;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 20px;
          border: none;
          box-shadow: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='page'>
      <h1>Power of Attorney</h1>

      <div class='section' style='text-align: left;'>
        City of
        {{city}},
        {{fullDateString}}.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        I, a citizen of Ukraine,
        <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>, born on
        {{birthDate}}, taxpayer registration card number
        {{taxId}}, place of residence registered at:
        {{address}}, passport No.
        {{passportNumber}}, issued by
        {{passportIssueAuthority}}
        on
        {{passportIssueDate}}, being fully aware of the meaning of my actions and in accordance with my free will, which
        fully corresponds to my inner intentions, do hereby authorize
        <strong>{{representativeName}}</strong>, born on
        {{representativeBirthDate}}, place of residence registered at:
        {{representativeAddress}},
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        TO BE MY REPRESENTATIVE in any
        {{authoritiesList}}, etc., regarding the
        <strong>SALE</strong>
        of the real estate property located in Ukraine at the address:
        <strong>{{propertyAddress}}</strong>, at a price and on terms at his/her own discretion, with the right to
        conclude and sign on my behalf purchase and sale agreements, and if necessary - preliminary agreements, deposit
        agreements, advance payment agreements, agreements on settlements under previously concluded agreements,
        agreements on introducing any amendments and/or additions to the aforementioned agreements, and agreements on
        the termination of the aforementioned agreements.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        For this purpose, I grant him/her the right to conduct negotiations, represent interests with all necessary
        powers in the relevant bodies, coordinate all issues arising in the course of exercising these powers, to be my
        representative in the relevant institutions and organizations on matters of obtaining the necessary documents
        related to water supply, electricity, gas, utilities, telephone services, as well as payment for these services,
        to submit documents and applications on my behalf to the relevant bodies and institutions, including those
        concerning my ownership of property by right of personal private property and my marital status, for my
        registration or de-registration (checking out, checking in), to receive necessary certificates and documents,
        including technical passports for the above-mentioned real estate, title documents, information from the State
        Register of Real Property Rights, Certificate (from the place of residence on family composition and
        registration), etc., to open and/or close accounts in any bank in Ukraine, to make non-cash payments, receive
        money due to me, to sign on my behalf on documents and for their receipt, to conclude and sign on my behalf all
        necessary civil contracts for maintenance services for the real estate, as well as to conclude and sign on my
        behalf purchase and sale agreements, preliminary agreements, deposit agreements, advance payment agreements,
        agreements on settlements under previously concluded agreements, agreements on introducing any amendments and/or
        additions to the aforementioned agreements, agreements on the termination of the aforementioned agreements; to
        pay on my behalf due payments: taxes, state duties, administrative fees, and other expenses, as well as to
        perform all other actions related to this power of attorney.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        This Power of Attorney is issued for a term of
        <strong>THREE YEARS</strong>
        and is valid until
        {{validUntilDate}}.
      </div>

      <div class='section'>
        I have read this power of attorney, its content is clear to me and corresponds to my will. Signed by me
        personally.
      </div>

      <div class='signature-section'>
        SIGNATURE _________________________________________________________________
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>